resource.title: Treatment plan for glioblastoma multiforme
resource.description: Comprehensive treatment plan including Surgery, Chemotherapy, Radiotherapy

resource.conclusion: Patient shows stable status for glioblastoma multiforme. Aisha Nguyen, a 57-year-old Asian female diagnosed with severe glioblastoma multiforme, underwent surgical resection followed by chemotherapy and radiotherapy. Currently in stable condition with regular follow-ups.
